title: #131 - (UTAH TRIP FLIP Special) Creighton Baird & Me
description: Adventurer, rock climber, internet star, & all around adrenaline enthusiast Creighton Baird hangs out w/ me and my Trip Flip crew on a houseboat to talk about pushing his girlfriend off a cliff, growing up Mormon, and creating The Corona Arch Swing a.k.a "Worlds Most Insane Epic Rope Swing" for Devon Supertramp.
